"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 382px; height: 373px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Edema of the Skin Edema of the skin is produced by lymphatic blockade. It appears as thickened skin with enlarged pores - the so-called peau d'orange (orange peel) sign. It is often seen first in the lower portion of the breast or areola.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
